# API base URL for the backend. Copy to .env and set if needed.
# - Web / iOS Simulator: defaults to http://localhost:8000/api/v1
# - If backend runs on 8001 (port 8000 in use): EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:8001/api/v1
# - Android Emulator: defaults to http://10.0.2.2:8000/api/v1 (use 10.0.2.2:8001 if backend on 8001)
# - Physical device: use your computer's LAN IP, e.g. EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://192.168.1.100:8000/api/v1
# After changing, restart Expo (npm start).
